FBIS4-34503 "drlat119_c_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-119 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 MEXICO Jalisco State Police To Fight Guadalajara Drug Bands Jalisco State Police To Fight Guadalajara Drug Bands PA2106023394 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0430 GMT 17 Jun 94 PA2106023394 Mexico City XEW Television Network Spanish BFN [From the "24 Hours" newscast] [Text] Today, the Government of Jalisco State approved the creation of a public security program for Guadalajara. Some 8,000 policemen will wage an all-out attack on narcotrafficking bands.
